    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国征收 10% 关税的期限即将到期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-10-tariffs-on-china-set-to-take-effect-as-deadline-passes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普计划与中国国家主席习近平举行会谈之际，美国已对所有中国商品征收 10% 的关税，拉开了与北京新一轮贸易战的序幕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-10-tariffs-on-china-set-to-take-effect-as-deadline-passes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党可以挽救其绿色声誉，但是它会做到吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-02-04/rosebank-jackdaw-fields-labour-could-save-its-green-reputation-but-will-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[没有哪个政党能够一下子兑现所有承诺，但基尔·斯塔默政府应该尽量避免干涉自己的事务。这包括对北海化石燃料生产的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-02-04/rosebank-jackdaw-fields-labour-could-save-its-green-reputation-but-will-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷豹路虎车主预计印度需求将在 6 月份复苏，关注美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/jlr-owner-sees-india-demand-revival-by-june-watching-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度政府为中产阶级减税 115 亿美元后，捷豹路虎的印度所有者发现，6 月底，这个世界第一人口大国的消费需求正在复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/jlr-owner-sees-india-demand-revival-by-june-watching-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 04:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税战为何人人皆输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/why-everyone-loses-in-trump-s-tariff-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚国际贸易和投资中心的普鲁登斯·戈登表示，中国、加拿大和墨西哥的企业不会面临贸易紧张局势升级的后果。她刚刚在《彭博社：亚洲贸易》节目中讨论了特朗普总统关税战中最大的输家。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/why-everyone-loses-in-trump-s-tariff-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 03:08:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税豁免预期推动香港中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-jump-on-hopes-of-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，美国政府将与北京举行会谈，引发市场对世界第二大经济体能够避免痛苦的关税上调的希望，香港中国股市随之飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-jump-on-hopes-of-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 02:52:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推迟对加拿大、墨西哥征收关税，铜和锌价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税的期限推迟一个月，导致铜和锌价格上涨，从而拖累美元走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税混乱助长避险需求，金价逼近纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税威胁及其随后的推迟增加了不确定性并支撑了避险需求，金价升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推迟一个月对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将对美国两大原油供应商征收关税的日期推迟了一个月，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因中国关税措施而回吐涨幅：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对中国征收更多关税的最后期限未达成协议后，亚洲股市抹去了涨幅，人民币小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
